### 방법 1: 배열로 트윗 추가 (권장)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/manual/add-tweets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "dio",
  "tweets": [
    "Shipping builds momentum. Momentum builds confidence. Confidence builds companies.",
    "You'll learn more in 2 weeks of launching than in 6 months of planning. Don't overthink it.",
    "Every failed release turned into a lesson I wouldn't trade. You only lose if you stop shipping.",
    "Building features is useless if nobody sees them. Shipping matters more.",
    "Perfect is the enemy of shipped. Start messy, iterate fast."
  ]
}

